                <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">The IRS has up to 5 years to audit your ERC claim. Many "pop-up" shops that filed these claims will be gone by the time you receive a notice. We are a permanent team here for the long haul.</p>
                <div style="height: 0.5rem; background: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;">
                    <div style="height: 100%; width: 80%; background: var(--primary); border-radius: 4px;"></div>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-light); margin-top: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">4 of 5 years remaining for most 2020/2021 claims</p>
