                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 1.5rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
                    <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--text-light);">Plus interest accruing daily</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card card-danger" style="border-color: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.2);">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #7f1d1d;">Unprotected Communications</h3>
                <p style="color: #991b1b; line-height: 1.7;">Communications with most ERC filers and consultants can be requested by the IRS. Make sure your defense team knows how to protect you.</p>
            </div>

